---

<style>
    .faq-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: auto;
    }

    /* Hide input */
    .faq-item input {
        display: none;
    }

    .faq-item {
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    /* Question Style */
    .faq-question {
        display: block;
        padding: 18px 20px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        cursor: pointer;
        position: relative;
        background: #f9f9f9;
        transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    .faq-question:hover {
        background: #eefaff;
    }

    /* Icon (+) */
    .faq-question::after {
        content: "+";
        position: absolute;
        right: 20px;
        top: 14px;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        transition: 0.35s;
    }

    /* Change icon to (â€“) when opened */
    .faq-item input:checked + .faq-question::after {
        content: "-";
        transform: rotate(180deg);
    }

    /* Answer box */
    .faq-answer {
        max-height: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #fff;
        color: #444;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        padding: 0 20px;
        transition: 0.35s;
        opacity: 0;
    }

    /* Smooth open */
    .faq-item input:checked ~ .faq-answer {
        padding: 20px;
        max-height: 999px; /* Large enough for any content */
        opacity: 1;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .faq-question {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    }
</style>

<Section
    title="Why Choose TabeMed"
    subTitle="Discover the benefits of using TabeMed for your medical appointment bookings."
>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <!-- FAQ Item -->
        <div class="faq-item">
            <input type="checkbox" id="faq1" />
            <label for="faq1" class="faq-question">
                What services do you provide?
            </label>

            <div class="faq-answer">
                We offer a wide range of professional medical and healthcare
                services tailored to your needs.
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item -->
        <div class="faq-item">
            <input type="checkbox" id="faq2" />
            <label for="faq2" class="faq-question">
                How can I book an appointment?
            </label>

            <div class="faq-answer">
                You can book an appointment online, by phone, or by visiting our
                clinic directly.
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item -->
        <div class="faq-item">
            <input type="checkbox" id="faq3" />
            <label for="faq3" class="faq-question">
                Do you accept insurance?
            </label>

            <div class="faq-answer">
                Yes, we work with most major insurance providers. Contact us for
                complete details.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Section>
